{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124690620217167872732084.jpeg/RJ_VAmyO68_mf4Ys5qij2Qim0txxrE6LHdau0x3WrtM\" alt=\"宏昌閣陳先生自備外骨骼輔助器上30樓單位。（黃偉民攝）\"><figcaption>宏昌閣陳先生自備外骨骼輔助器上30樓單位。（黃偉民攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124690617318772736136529.jpeg/wlTqz2MAQk8eU-uSYHsYATD274pF-sYfNxg-nTcYPp0\" alt=\"宏昌閣陳先生自備外骨骼輔助器上30樓單位。（黃偉民攝）\"><figcaption>宏昌閣陳先生自備外骨骼輔助器上30樓單位。（黃偉民攝）</figcaption></figure><p>中午12時半左右，陳先生和家人用行李箱推走家當，他說內裡滿載相簿、證件等等。今次陳先生特意斥資7000多元，在本地購入外骨骼輔助器：「有幫助，無咁辛苦。」至於入屋後的感受，他無奈說：「無咩嘢呀！又係咁！」黯然離去。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124692073224605696508127.jpeg/j488aFi-shE7dVeH_r5RqGo1sL83k9QXMVtkGDFbZBg\" alt=\"陳先生和家人搬走多個行李箱的物品。（黃偉民攝）\"><figcaption>陳先生和家人搬走多個行李箱的物品。（黃偉民攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124692076085252096093726.jpeg/KYGTZvwAnLT_RlZCFO7lZpJGyukJdMWt4hQNKOIUDSg\" alt=\"陳先生和家人搬走多個行李箱的物品。（黃偉民攝）\"><figcaption>陳先生和家人搬走多個行李箱的物品。（黃偉民攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124692078878789632745926.jpeg/_16ouyL-eFzSrjhK6VIUKrPUtj5xaV53VxQhYFcUIWA\" alt=\"陳先生和家人搬走多個行李箱的物品。（黃偉民攝）\"><figcaption>陳先生和家人搬走多個行李箱的物品。（黃偉民攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124692081588441088592031.jpeg/R2iUVJQZSdSxByvPxEA-v-BQMehoE9RWqHpkMah6ZDE\" alt=\"陳先生和家人搬走多個行李箱的物品。（黃偉民攝）\"><figcaption>陳先生和家人搬走多個行李箱的物品。（黃偉民攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124676125461581824509382.jpeg/P9w_SKKXbayMWbMKgeb1gGfxYhL0zqdGafm7zmn5u84\" alt=\"4月25日卓永興再到宏福苑視察居民上樓情況。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>4月25日卓永興再到宏福苑視察居民上樓情況。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124676128389337088413076.jpeg/FEwbIjkkrW_gxoemlf6Lq3XhR5jeSA0rS-a8RUvmvEU\" alt=\"4月25日卓永興再到宏福苑視察居民上樓情況。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>4月25日卓永興再到宏福苑視察居民上樓情況。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><p>上午11時半左右，卓永興由工作人員陪同下，再到宏福苑視察居民上樓情況。此前，他亦曾最少兩次到宏福苑，包括上樓了解確實狀況；他曾經表示會積極安排讓居民盡快再次上樓。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124650114741178368128937.jpeg/WmAsuOO-rBfz4_nyxdExfgctIAL6hOQYxEhANMRIQDQ\" alt=\"25日早上，宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民陸續上樓執拾。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>25日早上，宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民陸續上樓執拾。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124650118277107712368940.jpeg/y-bIWyVzhLwOpCCbcXHA7ac-kx-p-40zYe5s3WHubN0\" alt=\"25日早上，宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民陸續上樓執拾。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>25日早上，宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民陸續上樓執拾。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124650121754316800052148.jpeg/mZzlBZFo9aZf5zh4eGxpvxMJmBMY4RqYIt3wziLd8M4\" alt=\"25日早上，宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民陸續上樓執拾。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>25日早上，宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民陸續上樓執拾。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124650125739036672274659.jpeg/ToL_6x92CNOmdJPpxsT4P_DooMi7oZoyI64OjyOuDo8\" alt=\"25日早上，宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民陸續上樓執拾。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>25日早上，宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民陸續上樓執拾。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124650129430155264214765.jpeg/hy6CqiKQ2QLt5v5ZrFvPsV_09T390mH2yqLPscqiz7E\" alt=\"25日早上，宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民陸續上樓執拾。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>25日早上，宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民陸續上樓執拾。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124632012410458112210943.jpeg/HK-5wDLqCmPXUyk7pfv3xaDwYbtaKk3LxrK7E-CyuxM\" alt=\"居民帶備背囊、帆布袋和手拉車等上樓。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>居民帶備背囊、帆布袋和手拉車等上樓。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124632009600143360189437.jpeg/AH79NCVNPt-QANRLGloEF0z4mVphXleiONeutR7XrrU\" alt=\"居民帶備背囊、帆布袋和手拉車等上樓。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>居民帶備背囊、帆布袋和手拉車等上樓。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124632015111720960826013.jpeg/XweusX1z4C8o9He2WADNF9RFoPsl7tg1wh35j-Qd-Y8\" alt=\"居民帶備背囊、帆布袋和手拉車等上樓。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>居民帶備背囊、帆布袋和手拉車等上樓。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124632017846538240783195.jpeg/_gK1TIjGxS82jmPZ43jKOLHGrL1JxnmyejLEwVwyxME\" alt=\"居民帶備背囊、帆布袋和手拉車等上樓。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>居民帶備背囊、帆布袋和手拉車等上樓。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124632020753321984948163.jpeg/xrTSIxiu2RAtLmNQlfJ5dI_D9cCl6eJoxdPXaOPT12g\" alt=\"居民在社區中心登記後上樓。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>居民在社區中心登記後上樓。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124632002117505024841572.jpeg/tGFSKVYdz62LmXoIEqcX5TIXKYoGk6D-4Wmd6sdpneo\" alt=\"民安隊在場協助。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>民安隊在場協助。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124667344530968576430729.jpeg/62-cZBoAm_lIxZEElVkzgiNCFue-2BGLwqdZkOSnWZA\" alt=\"上午11時，有居民執拾後離開。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>上午11時，有居民執拾後離開。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124667348360499200584376.jpeg/NT5SqTwoutYAKGKiAaEC_Gi34HLg60GA5FuUJcJblCU\" alt=\"上午11時，有居民執拾後離開。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>上午11時，有居民執拾後離開。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124667351997091840942357.jpeg/qe0jN4773bZ2XxzcPjDiME9KgT0advocFAeSOjIHkjo\" alt=\"上午11時，有居民執拾後離開。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>上午11時，有居民執拾後離開。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260425/1124670082631340032235869.jpeg/UXLvk59FqjXoReUBZ7HLo1lAlrgHAXMeelSiMVxUojE\" alt=\"宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民執拾後離開。（翁鈺輝攝）\"><figcaption>宏仁閣和宏昌閣的居民執拾後離開。（翁鈺輝攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-25T10:37:01.049198+00:00","quality":{"score":2,"chars":773,"images":23,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}